spell_list.description: Prevents the berserker from dying when they take fatal damage. The berserker or one of their allies must strike a death blow within the duration of the triggered effect or the berserker will be unable to attack for a short duration. Higher ranks of this ability lower the base reuse time.
spell_list.description_pvp: Prevents the berserker from dying when they take fatal damage. The berserker or one of their allies must strike a death blow within the duration of the triggered effect or the berserker will be unable to attack for a short duration. Higher ranks of this ability lower the base reuse time.

effect_list.description: On death this spell will cast Rampager's Resiliance on caster.  Lasts for 45.0 seconds.
On termination, this will prevent the berserker from attacking unless the berserker or any member of their group or raid strikes a death blow.
Vision of Madness takes priority over this spell
Heals caster for 75.0% of max health
This effect cannot be critically applied.
Cannot be modified except by direct means
Grants a total of 1 trigger of the spell.

spell_list.name: Rampager's Resilience
